abstract: Tuesday: The Census Bureau says there might be 8.4 million people in New York City. That number used to be higher.
snippet: Tuesday: The Census Bureau says there might be 8.4 million people in New York City. That number used to be higher.
lead_paragraph: [Want to get New York Today by email? Here’s the sign-up.]

abstract: We know Big Tobacco’s playbook: It is targeting kids — and putting them in serious danger.
snippet: We know Big Tobacco’s playbook: It is targeting kids — and putting them in serious danger.
lead_paragraph: Any adult knows that if you want to get a child’s attention, there is no enticement like candy.
